  {
    "client_msg_id": "8ce24d2d-8cc6-42dc-af21-fa7c5e25b76c",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "\"Unicode exemplifies the tyranny of committees staffed with people who don't care how much damage they do as they erect their perfectly hypercomplex edifice.\"\n\nSounds like software development in general :/",
    "user": "UAVCC2X70",
    "ts": "1558904150.002300",
    "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "user_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "source_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "user_profile": {
      "avatar_hash": "ec35ac5b251f",
      "image_72": "https://avatars.slack-edge.com/2018-05-22/369438371830_ec35ac5b251f37e26aca_72.jpg",
      "first_name": "",
      "real_name": "Dan Cook",
      "display_name": "",
      "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
      "name": "dcook0819",
      "is_restricted": false,
      "is_ultra_restricted": false
    },
    "thread_ts": "1558597512.086500",
    "parent_user_id": "UEQ6M68H0",
    "channel_name": "linking-together",
    "channel_id": "C5U3SEW6A"
  },
  {
    "client_msg_id": "12005d62-22bc-4c8a-8d7e-6ae108226270",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "So many things in software have changed meaning or mean different things to different people. So it's kinda pointless to argue over what \"really\" means what.\n\nHOWEVER, the more serious problem is that things that have been claimed, proven, accepted, etc. regarding one definition, are then misapplied to the other. This is how TDD has somehow been \"proven\" successful and unsuccessful by different studies, etc.\n\nThat also makes it darn near impossible to communicate about the good and bad in software, because there are so many contradictory claims and attitudes, that it's easy to dismiss things as being opinionated or very wrong, or to accept things as \"proven\" or \"tried &amp; true\" that are actually not the thing that was proven.",
    "user": "UAVCC2X70",
    "ts": "1558908694.002500",
    "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "user_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "source_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "user_profile": {
      "avatar_hash": "ec35ac5b251f",
      "image_72": "https://avatars.slack-edge.com/2018-05-22/369438371830_ec35ac5b251f37e26aca_72.jpg",
      "first_name": "",
      "real_name": "Dan Cook",
      "display_name": "",
      "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
      "name": "dcook0819",
      "is_restricted": false,
      "is_ultra_restricted": false
    },
    "edited": {
      "user": "UAVCC2X70",
      "ts": "1558978657.000000"
